{"tid":1309700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民擬狙擊民建聯灣仔晚宴 伊利沙伯大廈保安封門兼鎖𨋢","createTime":"2019-07-12T10:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T10:42:54.000Z","uid":143343,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c5896f1dd317fa335cb1e7bbde3aef54073f015a","tid":1309700,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:18:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/inmediahk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Finmediahk%2F&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUym6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=6c48d182\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/inmediahk/</a><br />\n<br />\n【即時】（18:10）民建聯灣仔支部晚上在伊利沙白大廈舉行27週年會慶晚宴，有網民下午自發組團到場狙擊。<br />\n<br />\n伊利沙白大廈的保安更關閉商場的側門，獨媒和有線新聞記者欲乘坐貨𨋢前往餐廳的樓層，但保安稱不接受傳媒採訪，並將記者趕走及落閘。現時大廈大堂有近10名掛上「工作人員」的人士把守升降機，灣仔區議員兼民建聯灣仔支部主席鍾嘉敏亦在場打點一切。<br />\n<br />\n獨媒記者曾向新馥海景宴會廳查詢，職員表示餐廳已被包場，不接受街客預訂。<br />\n<br />\n#獨媒報導<br />\n追蹤最新消息：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/inmediahknet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finmediahknet&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUym6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=b6ad7276\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/inmediahknet</a><br />\n報導有價，請月捐支持<br />\n<a href=\"http://inmediahk.net/donate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finmediahk.net%2Fdonate&d=QCZ5VELzTGqQZzcx9zTUym6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=08c56a23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Finmediahk.net%2Fdonate&h=5011d3a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">inmediahk.net/donate</a>"},{"pid":"7423ab54d9922fb2439c87d7e7461d35c3ca42e4","tid":1309700,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:19:24.000Z","msg":"咁快保安咁嚴密"},{"pid":"3457835717d86b025d3b4ba18f3a35248dcdacc1","tid":1309700,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:19:56.000Z","msg":"睇黎真係有人 mon post"},{"pid":"a70a40e81e3de5872864aad6ec968e4535eb502c","tid":1309700,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"